title: Li Keqiang Sends Congratulatory Message to Khadga Prasad Oli for Assuming Office as Prime Minister ...
text: ( Source : Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the People's Republic of China ) On October 12 , 2015 , Premier Li Keqiang sent a congratulatory message to Khadga Prasad Oli for assuming office as the new Prime Minster of the Nepalese government . Li
